-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |TOP-N SORT                   |                      |1       |590         |
|1 |└─HASH JOIN                  |                      |1       |590         |
|2 |  ├─HASH JOIN                |                      |1       |259         |
|3 |  │ ├─NESTED-LOOP JOIN       |                      |1       |254         |
|4 |  │ │ ├─MERGE JOIN           |                      |1       |238         |
|5 |  │ │ │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN    |household_demographics|200     |12          |
|6 |  │ │ │ └─SORT               |                      |4       |209         |
|7 |  │ │ │   └─HASH JOIN        |                      |4       |209         |
|8 |  │ │ │     ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|customer_address      |4       |31          |
|9 |  │ │ │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN|customer              |1000    |93          |
|10|  │ │ └─TABLE GET            |customer_demographics |1       |16          |
|11|  │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |income_band           |10      |5           |
|12|  └─TABLE FULL SCAN          |store_returns         |3000    |80          |
===============================================================================
