|2 |  └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN    |           |1       |102         |
|3 |    ├─NESTED-LOOP JOIN  |           |4       |53          |
|4 |    │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN |item       |3       |11          |
|5 |    │ └─TABLE RANGE SCAN|store_sales|2       |16          |
|6 |    └─TABLE GET         |date_dim   |1       |16          |
===============================================================
